WEBVTT

00:01.070 --> 00:05.938
Sync and corrections by n17t01
www.addic7ed.com

00:05.939 --> 00:09.075
<i>Air and naval
forces of the United States</i>

00:09.109 --> 00:12.044
<i>launched a series of strikes</i>
<i>against terrorist facilities...</i>

00:12.079 --> 00:13.946
<i>Pan Am Flight 103 crashed
into the town of Lockerbie.</i>

00:13.981 --> 00:15.381
<i>He has sanctioned
acts of terror</i>

00:15.415 --> 00:18.050
<i>in Africa, Europe</i>
<i>and the Middle East.</i>

00:18.085 --> 00:20.753
<i>This will not stand, this
aggression against, uh, Kuwait.</i>

00:20.787 --> 00:22.455
<i>This relentless
pursuit of terror.</i>

00:22.489 --> 00:24.056
<i>We will make no distinction...</i>

00:24.091 --> 00:25.658
<i>The USS</i> Cole <i>was attacked</i>

00:25.692 --> 00:26.892
<i>while refueling in</i>
<i>the port of Aden.</i>

00:26.927 --> 00:28.794
This was an act of terrorism.

00:28.829 --> 00:31.330
It was a despicable
and cowardly act.

00:31.365 --> 00:33.766
<i>The next samba</i>
<i>we're going to swing for you</i>

00:33.800 --> 00:34.800
is one of the good old
favorites.

00:34.835 --> 00:37.403
...until something stops him.

00:37.437 --> 00:40.239
<i>It was right</i>
<i>in front of my eyes,</i>

00:40.273 --> 00:41.907
<i>and I never saw it coming.</i>

00:41.942 --> 00:44.977
<i>That plane crashed</i>
<i>into the World Trade Center.</i>

00:45.012 --> 00:47.480
<i>Thousands of people running.</i>

00:47.514 --> 00:51.484
We must and we will remain
vigilant at home and abroad.

00:57.357 --> 00:59.525
<i>You're the smartest</i>
<i>and the dumbest fucking person</i>

00:59.559 --> 01:01.694
<i>I've ever known.</i>

01:01.728 --> 01:03.329
<i>I'm not the
one who got it wrong.</i>

01:03.363 --> 01:05.464
<i>I'm the only one</i>
<i>who got it right.</i>

01:09.336 --> 01:11.203
<i>Take 'em.</i>

01:11.238 --> 01:12.972
<i>Take 'em all.</i>

01:19.993 --> 01:23.016
Homeland - 3x09
"Horse And Wagon"

01:24.718 --> 01:26.652
<i>Previously on</i> Homeland...

01:26.687 --> 01:27.853
I got plans for you.

01:27.888 --> 01:29.021
What plans?

01:29.056 --> 01:30.823
I'm gonna play you back
into Iran.

01:30.857 --> 01:33.859
From now on, you work for us.

01:33.894 --> 01:35.327
The Senator's made
some serious allegations.

01:35.362 --> 01:37.697
That you had Majid Javadi
in a safe house

01:37.731 --> 01:40.299
on American soil
and let him go.

01:40.333 --> 01:42.401
We debriefed him, turned him.

01:42.436 --> 01:44.270
He's ours.

01:44.304 --> 01:48.074
I've made a decision to give
the marriage another chance.

01:48.075 --> 01:49.727
_

01:50.644 --> 01:52.645
_

01:58.719 --> 02:00.219
So I told him something

02:00.253 --> 02:02.788
before you left...
about the Langley bomber.

02:02.823 --> 02:03.989
You mean Brody.

02:04.024 --> 02:05.558
No, that's just it.
It's not him.

02:05.592 --> 02:08.026
The bomber's the only way
to prove that Brody's innocent.

02:08.061 --> 02:09.929
Carrie, what the fuck
are you doing?

02:09.963 --> 02:11.864
Carrie, turn around now.

02:11.898 --> 02:14.567
This is your last warning.

02:17.604 --> 02:19.905
Got a gunshot wound
to the upper left bicep.

02:19.940 --> 02:21.807
significant bleeding.
Might have clipped an artery.

02:21.842 --> 02:24.376
Where the fuck is Saul?

